{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 15,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الحِجۡرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Hijr",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Rock",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 99,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 1803,
        "text": "艾列弗，倆目，拉儀。這些是天經——明白的《古蘭經》的節文。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1804,
        "text": "不信道者或許要希望他們原是歸順的。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1805,
        "text": "你聽任他們吃喝玩樂吧！你聽任他們受希望的誘惑吧！因為他們不久就會知道的。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1806,
        "text": "我不毀滅一個城市則已，但毀滅它，就有一個可知的定期。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1807,
        "text": "任何民族都不能先其定期而滅亡，也不能後其定期而淪喪。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1808,
        "text": "他們說：「受降示教誨的人啊！你確是一個瘋子。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1809,
        "text": "你怎不昭示我們一些天神呢？如果你是說實話的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1810,
        "text": "我只憑真理而降天神，到那時，他們是不蒙緩刑的。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1811,
        "text": "我確已降示教誨，我確是教誨的保護者。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1812,
        "text": "在你之前，我確已派遣了許多使者，去教化古代的各宗派。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1813,
        "text": "沒有一個使者來臨他們則已，但有使者來臨，他們都加以嘲笑。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1814,
        "text": "我這樣使愛好嘲笑深入罪人們的心。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1815,
        "text": "他們不信我的教誨，其實，古人的常道已逝去了。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1816,
        "text": "假若我為他們開闢一道天門，而他們從那道天門繼續登天，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1817,
        "text": "他們必定說：「我們的眼睛受蒙蔽了，不然，我們是中了魔術的民眾。」",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1818,
        "text": "我確已在天上創造了（十二）宮，我為觀察者而修飾天空。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1819,
        "text": "我保護著天，不許任何受詛咒的惡魔得以侵入，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1820,
        "text": "但竊聽的惡魔則有明顯的流星趕上它。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1821,
        "text": "我展開了大地，並把許多山岳安置在大地上，而且使各種均衡的東西生出來。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1822,
        "text": "我在大地上為你們和你們所不能供養者而創造了許多生活資料。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1823,
        "text": "每一種事物，我這裡都有其倉庫，我只依定數降下它。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1824,
        "text": "我派遣滋潤的風，我就從雲中降下雨水，以供給你們飲料，你們絕不是雨水的蓄藏者。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1825,
        "text": "我確是能使萬物生，能使萬物死的；我確是萬物的繼承者。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1826,
        "text": "我確已知道你們中先進的，我確已知道你們中後進的。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1827,
        "text": "你的主必定集合他們。他確是至睿的，確是全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1828,
        "text": "我確已用黑色的成形的黏土創造了人。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1829,
        "text": "以前，我曾用烈火創造了精靈。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1830,
        "text": "當時，你的主曾對天神們說：「我必定要用黑色的黏土塑造人像而創造人。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1831,
        "text": "當我把它塑成，而且把我的精神吹入他的塑像的時候，你們應當對他俯伏叩頭。」",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1832,
        "text": "隨後，天神們一同叩頭，",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1833,
        "text": "唯獨易卜劣廝不肯叩頭。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1834,
        "text": "主說：「易卜劣廝啊！你怎麼不叩頭呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1835,
        "text": "他說：「你用黑色黏土塑成人像而創造的人，我不該向他叩頭。」",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1836,
        "text": "主說：「你從這裡出去吧。因為你確是被放逐的。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1837,
        "text": "你必遭詛咒，直到報應日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1838,
        "text": "他說：「我的主啊！求你對我緩刑，直到人類復活之日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1839,
        "text": "主說：「你確是被緩刑",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1840,
        "text": "到可知的日期。」",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1841,
        "text": "他說：「我的主啊！你已判定我是迷誤的，所以我誓必在大地上以罪惡誘惑他們，我必定要使他們一同迷誤。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1842,
        "text": "除非他們中你所選拔的僕人。」",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1843,
        "text": "主說：「這是我應當維持的正路。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1844,
        "text": "我的僕人，你對他們絕無權力，除非那些順從你的迷誤者。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1845,
        "text": "火獄必定是他們全體的約定的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1846,
        "text": "火獄有七道門，每道門將收容他們中被派定的一部分人。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1847,
        "text": "敬畏者們必定在一些樂園和源泉之間，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1848,
        "text": "你們平平安安地進入樂園吧！」",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1849,
        "text": "我清除他們胸中的怨恨，他們將成為弟兄，在高榻上相對而坐。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1850,
        "text": "他們在那裡不感覺疲乏，他們絕不被逐出。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1851,
        "text": "你告訴我的僕人們，我確是至赦的，至慈的；",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1852,
        "text": "我的刑罰確是痛苦的。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1853,
        "text": "你應當對他們敘述易卜拉欣的客人們的故事。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1854,
        "text": "當時，他們進去見他，說：「祝你平安。」他說：「我們確是畏懼你們的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1855,
        "text": "他們說：「你不要畏懼，我們的確以一個聰明的男孩向你報喜。」",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1856,
        "text": "他說：「我已老邁，你們還向我報喜嗎？你們以甚麼向我報喜呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1857,
        "text": "他們說：「我們憑真理而向你報喜，所以你不要絕望。」",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1858,
        "text": "他說：「除迷誤者外，誰會絕望於真主的恩惠呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1859,
        "text": "他說：「使者們啊！你們有甚麼差事呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1860,
        "text": "他們說：「我們奉派去懲治一群犯罪的民眾。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1861,
        "text": "魯特的家族除外，我們確要把他們全都救出來；",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1862,
        "text": "但他的妻子除外，我們已預定她和其餘的人同受刑罰。」",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1863,
        "text": "當使者們來到魯特的家裡的時候，",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1864,
        "text": "他說：「你們確是一些陌生的人。」",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1865,
        "text": "他們說：「不然；我們把他們一向爭論的（刑罰）帶來給你了。",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1866,
        "text": "我們把真理帶來給你了，我們確是誠實的。",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1867,
        "text": "你應當帶著你的家族在深夜出行，你要跟在他們的後面，你們中的任何人也不要回頭看。你們應當往前走，一直走到你們奉命到達的地方。」",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1868,
        "text": "我啟示他這個判決：就是這等人，在早晨將被根除。",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1869,
        "text": "城裡的居民欣然而來，",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1870,
        "text": "他說：「這些是我的客人，你們不要凌辱我，",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1871,
        "text": "你們應當敬畏真主，你們不要差辱我。」",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1872,
        "text": "他們說：「難道我們沒有禁止你與世人往來嗎？」",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1873,
        "text": "他說：「這些是我的女兒，如果你們要幹甚麼。」",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1874,
        "text": "指你的壽命發誓，他們必將彷徨於自己的癲狂之中。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1875,
        "text": "吶喊聲在日出時襲擊了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1876,
        "text": "我使那個市鎮天翻地覆，並使陶石像雨點般降落在他們身上。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1877,
        "text": "對於能考察者，此中確有許多蹟象。",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1878,
        "text": "那個市鎮確是在一條仍然存在的道路上的。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1879,
        "text": "對於信道者，此中確有一種蹟象。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1880,
        "text": "那叢林的居民確是不義的，",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1881,
        "text": "故我懲治了他們。這兩個地方都在平坦的路上。",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1882,
        "text": "石谷的居民確已否認使者們。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1883,
        "text": "我確已把我的許多蹟象昭示他們，但他們背離了它。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1884,
        "text": "他們安全地鑿山為屋，",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1885,
        "text": "但吶喊聲在早晨襲擊了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1886,
        "text": "他們所謀求的，對於他們無濟於事。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1887,
        "text": "我只憑真理創造天地萬物，復活時是必定來臨的。所以你應當溫和地原諒眾人。",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1888,
        "text": "你的主確是創造萬物的主，確是全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1889,
        "text": "我確已賞賜你常常反復誦讀的七節經文和偉大的《古蘭經》。",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1890,
        "text": "你不要覬覦我所使他們中各等人所享受的事物，你不要為他們而悲哀。你應當溫和地對待信士們。",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1891,
        "text": "你說：「我確是坦率的警告者。」",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1892,
        "text": "那正如我所降示分配者們的（東西）一樣的，",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1893,
        "text": "他們把《古蘭經》分割成若干肢體。",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1894,
        "text": "指你的主發誓，我必將他們全體加以審問——",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1895,
        "text": "審問他們生前的行為。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1896,
        "text": "你應當公開宣布你所奉的命令，而且避開以物配主者。",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1897,
        "text": "在對付嘲笑者方面，我必使你滿足。",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1898,
        "text": "嘲笑者除真主外還崇拜別的神靈，不久他們就會知道了。",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1899,
        "text": "我確已知道你為他們的讕言而煩悶。",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1900,
        "text": "你應當讚頌你的主超絕萬物，你應當與眾人一起叩頭，",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1901,
        "text": "你應當崇拜你的主，直到那無疑的消息來臨。",
        "numberInSurah": 99,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      }
